        "setup": "Ask a Factorial company administrator to open the Factorial app and go to `Configuration` → `API` → `Create API KEY` (see [API Keys](https://apidoc.factorialhr.com/docs/api-keys) and [FAQ](https://apidoc.factorialhr.com/docs/faqs)). Copy the key value once and store it securely; it never expires and has full company access. Use it as the `x-api-key` request header with the raw key value, no prefix.",
