        "label": "Factorial OAuth 2 access token",
        "generateUrl": "https://api.factorialhr.com/oauth/applications",
        "setup": "Create or obtain a Factorial OAuth application in [production](https://api.factorialhr.com/oauth/applications) or [demo](https://api.eu2.demo.factorial.dev/oauth/applications), complete the authorization-code flow, and exchange the code for an access token at `https://api.factorialhr.com/oauth/token`. For multi-company partner apps, Factorial requires the official production OAuth application. The resulting token is the credential you send on requests as `Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>`. Tokens can be user-scoped or company-scoped; user tokens expire after about 1 hour, while company tokens do not expire until revoked.",
